body:
What if

This new theme isn’t @taylorswift giving us hints about ts7 but what “reputation” could have looked like if she already knew what stepping out of the spotlight would feel like? Or if the general public wasn’t so quick to demonize her behavior and music for the sake of absolutely nothing? Or if she never had to stand up for herself and other victims of assault in court? Or if no friend of hers twisted her mind and words? If she wasn’t betrayed. If she wasn’t captive.

I feel like these images being shared could be a fairytale portrayal of how perfect ts6 could have been if only she was outside of her cage? If only she found a rainbow and stopped living in the darkness… If she allowed the general public to have only what she wanted to give of herself and nothing else.


Or maybe it’s a parallel example of her rep costumes and outfits aligning with fairytale princesses as another extension of “Wildest Dreams?” 👀
